name: Shirt Grass (Team Upgrade)
description:
Upgrade one team you play in with Shirt Grass.

You can use any logo you want, it will change according to your shirt code.

You can use this item on one team, this team will then have the upgrade forever and the item will disappear from your inventory.

Upgrade the team in the User Panel.
